title: Combinations
htmlDescription:
Given non-negative integers m and n, generate all size m combinations of the integers from 0 (zero) to n-1 in sorted order (each combination is sorted and the entire table is sorted).

Example:

3 comb 5 is:

0 1 2
0 1 3
0 1 4
0 2 3
0 2 4
0 3 4
1 2 3
1 2 4
1 3 4
2 3 4
